{
  "text": "The following assertion is analogous to limit theorems which act on the whole axis for a sequence of partial sums of i.i.d.r.v.'s with a common not necessarily lattice distribution. We refer to [CITATION_1] for a comprehensive description of numerous limit theorems which act on the whole axis in the context of partial sums of i.i.d.r.v.'s. ",
